name: Pixar in Real Life
overview: This live action series brings iconic characters and moments from Pixar films into the real world. Filmed on location in and around New York City, the series surprises and delights real people in real locations when they least expect it.

episodes.name: Inside Out: Console in the Park
episodes.overview: Real people stumble upon the console from Inside Out, and are able to influence the emotions of different park goers. Watch what happens as they switch from Joy to Anger, Sadness, Fear, and Disgust!

episodes.name: Finding Dory: Aquarium Escape
episodes.overview: Dory and Hank surprise real aquarium visitors as they attempt an escape in a stroller.

episodes.name: WALL•E: Lost and Found
episodes.overview: People help a woman who lost her wedding ring & get a friendly surprise they won’t forget!

episodes.name: Toy Story: Traffic Cone Rescue
episodes.overview: Al’s Toy Barn opens a New York store, and the Toy Story gang attempts to rescue Woody.

episodes.name: Monsters, Inc.: Laugh Energy
